    <h2>Project goals</h2>
    Creation of web-based tool, enabling users to analyze selected data, in user-friendly way. The toll will be robust, to be able to handle diverse data sets. The aim is to collect and integrate the best practices for data processing and complement them, so that the resulting instrument will be able to present interesting findings, show deeper context, to connect the data with maps and other resources on the web.
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>Basic tasks</h2>
    Reading data from various formats (CSV, XML, SQL) presentation of basic variables (entities, tables, examples of values), user-driven data analysis (mean, median, deviation, range of values, connection based on similar texts, information extraction) presentation of the results in the form of graphs and tables, linking data with other sources (Web API, other data sources, encyclopedias)
